1- first get the mac address and store it in a variable (any downloaded package remains with the program)
2- get the instant pc user-name using os library (os.getlogin())
3- build the email components (subject, body ... etc) and remon as permenant reciver
4- build send-email functions that accepts all email components as parameters
5- as soon as the function called it's get the mac address of user's pc then sends it to remon by email
